query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS emailDeliverability (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  employerId INT NOT NULL,
  date DATE NOT NULL,
  totalSent INT DEFAULT 0,
  totalDelivered INT DEFAULT 0,
  hardBounces INT DEFAULT 0,
  softBounces INT DEFAULT 0,
  spamComplaints INT DEFAULT 0,
  unsubscribes INT DEFAULT 0,
  deliveryRate INT DEFAULT 0,
  bounceRate INT DEFAULT 0,
  spamRate INT DEFAULT 0,
  senderScore INT DEFAULT 100,
  reputationStatus ENUM('excellent', 'good', 'fair', 'poor', 'critical') DEFAULT 'good',
  createdAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  updatedAt TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  UNIQUE KEY unique_employer_date (employerId, date),
  INDEX idx_employer (employerId),
  INDEX idx_date (date),
  INDEX idx_reputation (reputationStatus),
  FOREIGN KEY (employerId) REFERENCES employers(id) ON DELETE CASCADE
) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8mb4 COLLATE=utf8mb4_unicode_ci;
